<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover" />
<title>双AI穿墙贪吃蛇</title>
<style>
  html, body {
    margin: 0;
